name: Tabersonine 16-hydroxylase 2
reaction: (-)-tabersonine + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = 16-hydroxytabersonine + H(+) + H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: Secologanin synthase 2
reaction: loganin + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = H(+) + 2 H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] + secologanin

name: Secologanin synthase 2
reaction: O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] + secologanin = 2 H(+) + H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] + secoxyloganin

name: 7-deoxyloganic acid hydroxylase
reaction: 7-deoxyloganate + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = H(+) + H2O + loganate + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: Drimenol monooxygenase
reaction: (5S,9S,10S)-drim-7-en-11-ol + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = (5S,10S)-(9R)-7-drimene-11,12-diol + H(+) + H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: Cytochrome P450 monooxygenase mpaDE
reaction: 4,6-dihydroxy-2-(hydroxymethyl)-3-methylbenzoate + H(+) = 5,7-dihydroxy-4-methylphthalide + H2O

name: Cytochrome P450 monooxygenase mpaDE
reaction: 5-methylorsellinate + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = 4,6-dihydroxy-2-(hydroxymethyl)-3-methylbenzoate + H(+) + H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: Alstonine synthase
reaction: A + ajmalicine + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = AH2 + H(+) + 2 H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] + serpentine

name: Alstonine synthase
reaction: A + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] + tetrahydroalstonine = AH2 + alstonine + H(+) + 2 H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: Iridoid oxidase
reaction: (+)-cis-trans-nepetalactol + 3 O2 + 3 reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = 7-deoxyloganetate + 4 H(+) + 4 H2O + 3 oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: Parthenolide synthase
reaction: (+)-costunolide + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = H(+) + H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] + parthenolide

name: 3-beta-hydroxylase
reaction: (+)-costunolide + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = 3beta-hydroxycostunolide + H(+) + H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: 3-beta-hydroxylase
reaction: O2 + parthenolide + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = 3beta-hydroxyparthenolide + H(+) + H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: Costunolide synthase
reaction: germacra-1(10),4,11(13)-trien-12-oate + O2 + reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = (+)-costunolide + 2 H2O + oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]

name: Germacrene A hydroxylase
reaction: (+)-(R)-germacrene A + 3 O2 + 3 reduced [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase] = germacra-1(10),4,11(13)-trien-12-oate + 4 H(+) + 4 H2O + 3 oxidized [NADPH--hemoprotein reductase]
